    "To achieve this goal, diverse signalling schemes corresponding to the underlying radar waveforms have been developed.",
    "Moreover, the receive signal techniques are also critical to sensing performance.",
    "In contrast, communication-centric ISAC techniques focus on modifying the communication waveforms for sensing, and how to extract the critical information of the target from echo is very important.",
    "Different from the abovementioned two categories of ISAC techniques, the joint-design ISAC techniques design the ISAC waveform, beamforming, and transceiver from foundational principles, enjoying the advantages of high flexibility.",
    "Nevertheless, they usually involve the complex optimization problems to balance the communication and sensing functionalities."
